      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sorted E46 M3 powered by the iconic S54B32 inline-six. This unit features a fully addressed VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. The high-revving 3.2L engine breathes through individual throttle bodies and is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Equipped with a factory M-Variable differential lock and refreshed suspension bushings, the handling remains sharp and predictable. Minor cosmetic wear present, but the drivetrain is robust and track-ready. A focused enthusiast's build.",
